MtYXJlLWRpc2FwcG9pbnRlZD9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMjEzMjJfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtP=
WVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMjEyMTMmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWdu=
PW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB65e988e7" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">lax customer data protections</a>=C2=A0and=C2=A0<a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29972411.258527/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
Ymxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDktMjEvc2Vhd29ybGQtcy1zdHJ=
hbmdlLXNlY3VyaXRpZXMtZnJhdWQ_Y21waWQ9QkJEMTIxMzIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZG=
l1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIxMjEzJnV0bV9jYW1wY=
Wlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1b4e37fa" target=3D"_blank" st=
yle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-widt=
h: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgroun=
d-color: #ccc;">mistreatment of orcas</a>=C2=A0can all be transmuted into s=
ecurities fraud.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here the underlying bad deed that was transmut=
ed into securities fraud was=C2=A0<em>also=C2=A0securities fraud</em>=E2=80=
=94Goldman said it put customers first, then it=C2=A0did a fraud on the Aba=
cus CDO buyers, then it got caught, then its stock dropped=E2=80=94but that=
 is just a coincidence. If instead of defrauding the Abacus CDO buyers Gold=
man had murdered them, that would not have been securities fraud with respe=
ct to the Abacus CDO buyers (it would have been murder), but it would still=
 have been securities fraud with respect to Goldman=E2=80=99s shareholders =
(if the stock dropped after Goldman was charged with murder).</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Similarly, here, the underlying bad deed was (=
allegedly) running a fraud at a crypto exchange, which certainly=C2=A0<em>l=
ooks like </em>securities fraud, but might not actually be.=C2=A0But it doe=
sn=E2=80=99t matter; if you have shareholders, any sort of fraud is also se=
curities fraud.</p>
